tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE partnerships (
  partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  partner_name VARCHAR(255),
  collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    partnership_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    initiative_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    collaboration_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT REFERENCES partnerships(partnership_id),
    campaign_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    platform TEXT NOT NULL,
    budget DECIMAL,
    status TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    company_name VARCHAR(255),
    contact_person VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    collaboration_type VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE,
    budget DECIMAL(10, 2),
    status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE partners (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partner_name VARCHAR(255),
    industry_type VARCHAR(100),
    contact_person VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(15),
    location VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE collaborations (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    partnership_id INT,
    campaign_id INT,
    partner_id INT,
    collaboration_status VARCHAR(20),
    collaboration_notes TEXT
);
